## Tahap 1 — Persiapan Environment (Docker Compose)

### 1.1 Instalasi Awal

- Install **Docker Desktop** di Windows (dengan WSL2 backend)
- Buat folder kerja project, contoh: `C:\Users\namamu\nama-project`
- Clone repo ini, lalu salin template environment variable:
  ```bash
  cp .env.example .env
  ```
- Isi seluruh nilai di `.env` dengan kredensial milikmu sendiri (lihat komentar di tiap baris `.env.example` sebagai panduan)

### 1.2 File `docker-compose.yml`

> Seluruh kredensial di bawah dibaca dari file `.env` — **tidak ada nilai rahasia yang di-hardcode** di file ini.

```yaml
services:
  waha:
    image: devlikeapro/waha
    container_name: waha
    ports:
      - "3000:3000"
    environment:
      - WHATSAPP_DEFAULT_ENGINE=NOWEB
      - WHATSAPP_HOOK_URL=http://n8n:5678/webhook/vps-order
      - WHATSAPP_HOOK_EVENTS=message
      - WAHA_DASHBOARD_ENABLED=true
      - WAHA_DASHBOARD_USERNAME=${WAHA_DASHBOARD_USERNAME}
      - WAHA_DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=${WAHA_DASHBOARD_PASSWORD}
      - WAHA_API_KEY=${WAHA_API_KEY}
      - WHATSAPP_RESTART_ALL_SESSIONS=true
      - WHATSAPP_START_SESSION=default
    volumes:
      - waha_data:/app/.sessions
    dns:
      - 8.8.8.8
      - 8.8.4.4
    restart: unless-stopped

  n8n:
    image: n8nio/n8n
    container_name: n8n
    ports:
      - "5678:5678"
    environment:
      - WEBHOOK_URL=${WEBHOOK_URL}
      - NODE_FUNCTION_ALLOW_BUILTIN=*
      - NODE_FUNCTION_ALLOW_EXTERNAL=*
      - N8N_BLOCK_ENV_ACCESS_IN_NODE=false
      - N8N_BASIC_AUTH_ACTIVE=${N8N_BASIC_AUTH_ACTIVE}
      - N8N_BASIC_AUTH_USER=${N8N_BASIC_AUTH_USER}
      - N8N_BASIC_AUTH_PASSWORD=${N8N_BASIC_AUTH_PASSWORD}
      - GENERIC_TIMEZONE=Asia/Jakarta
      - TZ=Asia/Jakarta
      # Secret berikut dipakai lewat $env di dalam Code node / expression n8n
      - GEMINI_API_KEY=${GEMINI_API_KEY}
      - GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=${GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL}
      - GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PRIVATE_KEY=${GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PRIVATE_KEY}
      - GOOGLE_SPREADSHEET_ID=${GOOGLE_SPREADSHEET_ID}
      - QRIS_RECIPIENT_NAME=${QRIS_RECIPIENT_NAME}
      - WAHA_API_KEY=${WAHA_API_KEY}
    volumes:
      - n8n_data:/home/node/.n8n
    dns:
      - 8.8.8.8
      - 8.8.4.4
    restart: unless-stopped
    depends_on:
      - waha

  cloudflared:
    image: cloudflare/cloudflared:latest
    container_name: cloudflared
    command: tunnel --no-autoupdate run --token ${CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL_TOKEN}
    restart: unless-stopped
    depends_on:
      - n8n

volumes:
  waha_data:
  n8n_data:
```

### 1.3 File `.env.example` (template — salin jadi `.env` dan isi sendiri)

```env
# ===== WAHA =====
WHATSAPP_HOOK_EVENTS=message
WAHA_DASHBOARD_USERNAME=admin
WAHA_DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=ganti_dengan_password_kuat
WAHA_API_KEY=ganti_dengan_api_key_acak

# ===== n8n =====
N8N_BASIC_AUTH_ACTIVE=true
N8N_BASIC_AUTH_USER=admin
N8N_BASIC_AUTH_PASSWORD=ganti_dengan_password_kuat
WEBHOOK_URL=https://your-domain.example.com/

# ===== Cloudflare Tunnel =====
CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL_TOKEN=isi_token_tunnel_dari_dashboard_cloudflare

# ===== Google Gemini API =====
GEMINI_API_KEY=isi_gemini_api_key_kamu

# ===== Google Service Account (Sheets) =====
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=nama-bot@nama-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nISI_PRIVATE_KEY_DISINI\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
GOOGLE_SPREADSHEET_ID=isi_id_spreadsheet_kamu

# ===== Konfigurasi Bisnis =====
QRIS_RECIPIENT_NAME=Nama_Sesuai_QRIS_Kamu
```

> ⚠️ **Jangan pernah commit file `.env`** ke repository — sudah otomatis diabaikan lewat `.gitignore`.

### 1.4 Menjalankan Container

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

### Catatan Penting yang Dipelajari

- `WHATSAPP_HOOK_URL` menggunakan hostname docker internal (`n8n:5678`), bukan `localhost` — ini hanya berfungsi jika WAHA dan n8n berada di **network docker yang sama** (otomatis terjadi kalau didefinisikan di `docker-compose.yml` yang sama)
- Volume `waha_data` dan `n8n_data` **wajib** ada supaya session WhatsApp & data workflow tidak hilang setiap kali container di-restart
- `WHATSAPP_RESTART_ALL_SESSIONS=true` membantu WAHA otomatis reconnect session setelah container restart
- `N8N_BLOCK_ENV_ACCESS_IN_NODE=false` diperlukan supaya Code node & expression n8n bisa mengakses `$env.NAMA_VARIABEL` (lihat catatan keamanan di bagian bawah)

